todo list: list 
description: string
date: string 
item index: integer

0. print the menu
- display the different choices
- take user input for which choice they want to perform
1. print todo list
- display all tasks
2. add 
- add a new task
    - collect description 
    - collect date
3. remove
- delete task from list
4. check off
- adding the word done after the task
5. exit
- quit the program